\id 1TI - Dũya Translation Project
\h 1 Utimoti
\toc1 Ubvur uwu inggbaashia Uburhu aka atsɛnge Utimoti
\toc2 1 Utimoti
\toc3 1Uti
\mt2 Ubvur uwu inggbaashia Uburhu aka atsɛnge
\mt1 Utimoti
\imt1 Utsutson ri itsi ubvur Utimoti uwu inggbaashia
\ip Awu Uburhu uner itser Uyesu atsɛng ubvur uwurɛ. Abɔɔ agɛ atsɛng ubvur uwurɛ ru Umakidoniya ra amɛk aki 63-67 udzur ru unumkpi umbɔ aka amar Uyesu.
\ip Uburhu amesuwe Utimoti ru udĩ Uteijee. Unga abɔre Utimoti ru Uafisa, ru Utimoti afituwe abika adɔsa na amesuwe umbɔ imesi idzidzɛrhe utsur abɔɔ arhɛm umbɔ nggu imesi igbɛrangwĩ. Uburhu atsɛng ubvur uwurɛ amesuwe Utimoti udĩkpi unga aka atɔ̃ itser umɔ.
\ip Ru ubvur ha, Uburhu agbaashia amesuwe imesa ri itsi imesi igbɛrangwĩ iyiriyɛ iki iwiwengge nggu imesi idzidzɛrhe unga aka amesuwe. Ubvur ha umesuwe imesa ri itsi idzowe igɔng, ni imesuwe ikpũ itseryɛ iki imɛ̃ɛ̃ anggbaashi ra abika adɔsa atɔ̃, nu ikɛi ikpũ amɛnkɛ aka amɛ̃ɛ̃ umbɔ awe ra ake. Ri imimasha, umbɔ adzowe Utimoti itsũwã ri itsi udĩkpi unga aka iwu uner uku utɔ̃itser idzidzɛrhe iyi Ukiristo nu itseryɛ unga aka awerangge ri ikikɔng abika adɔsa.
\iot Abinkɛ aka awe umɔ
\io1 Utsutson ri itsi ubvur ha \ior (1.1-2)\ior*
\io1 Imesa ri itsi abika adɔsa nu anggbaashimbɔ \ior (1.3—3.16)\ior*
\io1 Imesa ru Utimoti ri itsi itsernga \ior (4.1—6.21)\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ubvur uwirɛ udzeku umum, Uburhu, uner itser Ukiristo Uyesu ri itsitsu Unum Uwuku Ufɔrh umɛn nu Ukiristo Uyesu ifosamɛn.
\p 
\v 2 Uzĩ ru Utimoti, uze ungwɛ̃mum uwu idzidzɛrhe ri imangmang.
\p Unum Utɛ nu Ukiristo Uyesu Uteijeemɛn ama adzaa ungo imimuta, nu atorh nu ididɔɔr.
\s1 Itsitsɛrhe izĩ ra abi imesa igbɛrangwĩ
\p 
\v 3 Ru nyaka umum iki ishɔ̃rhã ungo ri ivangyɛ umum iki iwuri izĩ Umakidoniya, usei ru Uafisa, nu utsu anera abɔɔ aneke imesuwe igbɛrangwĩ.
\v 4 Udɛyiwe umbɔ niba atsumbɔ amɛnmbɔ ra atsutson nu idɔsa atsutsok aka asi imaake. Ikpũ arherhe akɛrɛ isi itsu umbɔ atɔ̃mbɔ itser Unum iki iwe ru ubok imangmang, bɔr iwuri ikũ uning aba.
\v 5 Ubinkutsu umum itsuka umbi akɛrɛ ha umum ibee abika adɔsa kishoo awe ru ibibema, iki idzek ra amɛn aka atɛn nu amɛn aka aze nu imangmang idzidzɛrhe.
\v 6 Abɔɔ aka abɔrukumbɔ akɛrɛ ha na atsimbɔ idɔsa arherhe aka atãrhã.
\v 7 Umbɔ abee iwe abika amesuwe Íkpem Umusa. Awu abika amesuwe nggu ikeramɛn ugɛɛ ahwɛngmbɔ ubinkpi umbɔ aka ani imesuwe, bɔr nggayɛ umbɔ asi ihwɛngmbɔ abinkɛ umbɔ aki irherhe.
\p 
\v 8 Umɛn ihwɛngmɛn ugɛ Íkpem ize anera aba atɔ̃mbɔ itser nggu ngge ru utsĩndĩ uku uze.
\v 9 Umɛn ikɛi ihwɛngmɛn ugɛ asi ingwɛ̃mbɔ Íkpem ra abika arhurhika bɔr ra abika akpɛ̃ idɔsi Íkpem, na asoyi amɛn, abirabɛ aka asi idɔsumbɔ Unum, nu abika akorha arhim, asi isarmbɔ na ashimbɔ ri iwei Unum, nu abika afɛyi atei use ayisumbɔ, abika afɛr aner,
\v 10 nu abika atoma-dak, nu akatsak abika arha akatsak nu akatsɛrh abika arha akatsɛrh, abika agoyi na agoyiwe agãrhã, nu abi igbɛrangwĩ, nu abi ideka igbɛrangwĩ, nu kishoo abinkɛ aka awuweke nggu imesa iyi idzidzɛrhe.
\v 11 Imesa ha idzek ri Isarhe Iyiki Ize ri itsi ikpikpoi Unum uwu idorh aka atsuka ru ubokmum.
\s1 Imimutu Uteijee ru Uburhu
\p 
\v 12 Umum itar uwɛɛ ru Ukiristo Uyesu Uteijeemɛn, uwuku udzaa umum iker, unga anyanga umum iwe uner idzidzɛrhe, unga atsuka umum ri itsernga.
\v 13 Nu ngge iki iwe ugɛ umum irhenumum Unum, idzowukũ uver ra abika adɔsu Uyesu ni iwe atsotso ru umbɔ ishaa, bɔr unga adɛyiwa umum atorh ubinkutsu umum ikorhe ri ida ihwihwɛng nu isheri imangmang.
\v 14 Imimuta Uteijeemɛn iwupa ru umum akarhãrhã, urhɔnga nggu imangmang nu ibibema akirakɛ aka awe ru Ukiristo Uyesu.
\p 
\v 15 Arherhe idzidzɛrhekɛ aka imɛ̃ɛ̃ anera kishoo ayɛi nggu aboka avaa. Ukiristo Uyesu aba ifɔrh abi arhim ru upfung, nu umum iki iwu undzumu uner arhim.
\v 16 Bɔr ngge itsú Ukiristo Uyesu agũ atorh umum, umum iki iwu ra arhim inang ubɛn unera ru umbɔ, ngge itsú ru umum unga awuri idɛyiwe undzumu idɔng amɛnnga ru umum ima iwu utsar ri kishoo abirabɛ aka awe ru imangmang ru unga na akpo urhɛ uwu ugbagbaa.
\v 17 Unum aka awu Uyɛrhe ugbagbaa, uwuruwi aka asi íkpea, asi ínyãmbɔ unga, unga aka awu Unum ikiyikanga, uneke igɔng nu ikpikpoi iwe nggu unga ugbagbaa nu ugbagbaa. Iwerimi.
\p 
\v 18 A ungwɛ̃mum Utimoti, abinkɛ umum iki idɛyiwa ungo, awu uku kpengkpeng nggu abinkɛ anera abɔɔ aka agũ ru Unum na arherhe ri itsingo. Ungo uba udɔsungo ake, ungo udɛ̃ɛ̃ utango iwa iyiki ize ha,
\v 19 nu ukpɔm imangmango ri ifɛrhkɔyɛ iki itsu ungo ukorhu ubin uku uze. Abɔɔ akpɛ̃mbɔ abin akɛrɛ ha na adakuwe imangmangmbɔ.
\v 20 Ra abi ha awu Uhimeniyu nu Uarhekzanda, abirabɛ umum iki idzowe umbɔ ru Ushaitan umbɔ amesi ineke irhenu Unum.
\c 2
\s1 Itsũwã ri idzowe igɔng
\p 
\v 1 Nggee ubin uku unang, umum ifituwa ugɛ, àka afɛne-Num ra adɔka ru ubɛn utsĩndĩã, na atang awɛɛ ru Unum ru ubɛn unera.
\v 2 Àka afɛn-Num riminɛ ra ayɛrhe nu kishoo abi ijee, ugɛ umɛn ima isei uku ughwɔɔw ri ibibɛk idɔngamɛn, ri iwei Unum nu isisar.
\v 3 Akɛrɛ ha aze, nu Unum Uwuku Ufɔrh umɛn agũibɛn ake.
\v 4 Unga abee anera kishoo akpo ififɔrh na aba ahwɛng idzidzɛrhe.
\v 5 Ubinkutsu Unum awu unying, na akpurha awu unying aka awe ra ateu Unum nu anera, uner ha unga awu Ukiristo Uyesu.
\v 6 Unga adzowe itsinga ififai ra anera na ashɔɔte kishoo. Unum adekuwa umɛn akɛrɛ uku kpengkpeng ri ivang hã.
\v 7 Akɛrɛ ha atsu umbɔ asɛng umum iwu uner udũwã ni iwu uner itser Uyesu. Nu ikɛi iwu uner uwuku umesuwe imangmang idzidzɛrhe ra atsen abi Uyahuda. Umum irherhe idzidzɛrhe isi igbɛrmum angwĩ.
\p 
\v 8 Umum ibee anera ubɛn ananga abera abok aka asar ri ifɛn-Num, akorha ake ri ishera avɔm use uning.
\p 
\v 9 Ikɛi umum ibee akatsɛrh atsim atorhakɛ aka imɛ̃, na akpɔm imormbɔ na akpɔm atsimbɔ. Niba afɛrmbɔ uhwɛk akarhãrhã ri igbisha atsimbɔ, uzinarhi use abinato use atorho imang,
\v 10 bɔr umbɔ akorhe iyiki ize, iyiriyɛ iki iwu uku kpengkpeng ru nyaku akatsɛrh abɛ aka iwe ri iwei Unum.
\p 
\v 11 Neke ukutsɛrh ayɛi imesa ukutata nu undzumu idzowe itsinga.
\v 12 Umum isi inekukũ ukutsɛrh ijee iyiki imesuwe use awe ru ijee ni itsi ukutsak, awu ufang unga anukutata.
\v 13 Ubinkutsu agbaashia amunu Uadamu mɔcɛ Uhawa'u.
\v 14 Ikɛi asi irhɛma Uadamu, bɔr arhɛm ukutsɛrh ha na awe uner arhim.
\v 15 Bɔr awuri ifɔrh ukutsɛrh ru ubok imar awɛkaci, umbɔ aba azɛ̃rhũmbɔ ri imangmang, ibibema nu isisar, nggu ikpɔm itsi.
\c 3
\s1 Uwuku umɛ̃ɛ̃ iwe unggbaashi // ri ididɔsa
\p 
\v 1 Arherha akɛrɛ awu idzidzɛrhe, unera aba abee iwu unggbaashi ri ikikɔng abika adɔsu Uyesu, abee itser iyiki ize.
\v 2 Awu ufang unggbaashi ashia ru ubin umbɔ aka ichaia unga, awu uner utsɛrha unying, awu uner uwuku ukpɔm itsinga ra abina kishoo, awu unerwi anera aki idzowe unga imor, awu uner uwuku uyɛi atsen, uwuku uhwɛng imimesuwe.
\v 3 Asi íwea uner uwuku udzowe itsinga ra adɛ, asi íwea uner uwuku ufɛmbok bɔr awu uner uwuku ududɔɔr, asi íwea ru uning, ikɛi asi íwea uner uwuku ubemu uhwɛk.
\v 4 Awu ufang unga awu unerwi aka idɛ̃ɛ̃ akpɔm iyanga, na atsu awɛkacinga adɔsa arherhenga na adzowe imor ru unga.
\v 5 Unera aba asi idɛ̃ɛ̃ akpɔma iyanga, awuri ikorha aguse na adɛ̃ɛ̃ akpɔm abika adɔsu Unum?
\v 6 Awu ufang asi íwea uner uwuku ufa aka ani idzipa, use unga awe ru iberi itsinga umbɔ atsu unga uvau ru nyaka Undenggũ ha.
\v 7 Awu ufang unga awu unerwi aka awe ru ideka iyiki ize ra asu abirabɛ aka asi idɔsumbɔ Uyesu, utsur ngge itsu unga awea ubin atsa na agbaa ru unggurhi Undenggũ.
\p 
\v 8 Rimi hã ikɛi udikin awu uner imor ra anera, asi íwea uner ingwĩa avaa. Ikɛi asi íwea unerwi aka inyangi itsinga adzowe ra adɛ, use abika abee uhwɛk ru udĩ uku ubewe.
\v 9 Awu ufang umbɔ akpɔm imesa idzidzɛrheyɛ Unum aka adeyiwa nu ifɛrhkɔmbɔ iyiki itɛn iki idɛyiwe ugɛ ashimbɔ ra avau.
\v 10 Awu ufang umbɔ avira umbɔ. Ubin uvau uba ushimgbɔ ru umbɔ, uneke umbɔ atɔ̃ itser ha.
\p 
\v 11 Rimi hã atsɛ̃mbɔ awu abika amɛ̃ iyɛi imor, asi íwembɔ abika anyata anera, na abirabɛ aka akpɔm atsimbɔ, awe ru idzidzɛrhe ra abina kishoo.
\p 
\v 12 Uwuku utɔ̃itser udikin awu ufang unga awu ru utsɛrha unying na ahwɛng ikpɔm awɛkacinga nu aner iyanga arhika.
\v 13 Abika atɔ̃ itser iyiki ize aka isaka akpombɔ atsok aka aze na aker amɛn arherhi imangmangmbɔ ru Ukiristo Uyesu.
\p 
\v 14 Umumwi ifosi iba ru ungo ifetem, bɔr umum itsɛnga ungo ubvur uwurɛ ngge itsú,
\v 15 umum ĩba isi ĩbamum ifetem, ungo uwuri uhwɛngo abinkɛ anera aka ikorhe ra abi iya Unum. Ikirikɛ iki iwu ikikɔng abika adɔsu Unum uwu urhɛ, aka awe ugban na atarh idzidzɛrhe.
\v 16 Irhirhusa ishingge, abinkɛ Unum aka adɛyiwa umɛn awu abin idzeu, ugɛ,
\q1 Ukiristo adzeka ri iyor,
\q2 Ipfu-Num idɛyiwa igɛ unga arhika,
\q1 ípfu itser-Num inyãngge unga,
\q2 abika adɔsa adzowe isarhanga
\q2 ra anera ri idũa kishoo,
\q1 awe ru imangmang ru unga ru upfunga,
\q2 ashupa unga afafã ri ikpikpoi.
\c 4
\s1 Imesa izĩ ru Utimoti
\p 
\v 1 Ipfu-Num irherhe ra awiya igɛ ivanga niyɔ ibarɔ abɔɔ awuri inekukumbɔ imangmang. Awuri idzowe atsimbɔ ri Ípfu igbɛrangwĩ nu imesa iyiki idzeki ípfu iyiki ibewe.
\v 2 Ikpũ imesa ha idzeku abi ukpukpeta abika agbɛrangwĩ, abirabɛ ifɛrhkɔmbɔ iyiki ihwɛng iyiki ize nu iyiki ibewe iki ikpengge.
\v 3 Umbɔ atsu anera akpɛ̃mbɔ ipfuna na atsu umbɔ aneke igha abingha akɔɔ. Akirakɛ Unum amuna umbɔ aka iyɛi ake nggu itar uwɛɛ ra abika awe ru imangmang na ahwɛng idzidzɛrhe.
\v 4 Bɔr ubɛn abinkɛ Unum aka amuna awu azeze, niba akpɛ̃mbɔ ubɛn ubin, umbɔ aba ayɛimbɔ ake nggu itar uwɛɛ,
\v 5 ubinkutsu aka asare ake nggu Arherhu-Num nu ifɛn-Num.
\p 
\v 6 Ungo uba umesukɔ angwɛ̃mɛn akɛrɛ ha, ungo uwuri iwu uner itser uku uze uwu Ukiristo Uyesu, uwuruwi umbɔ aka amesuwe ri irhɛm idzidzɛrhe iyi imangmang nu imesa iyiki ize iyiriyɛ ungo uku udɔsa.
\v 7 Niba ukhapungo nggu atsutson aka asi idzowuke imor ru Unum, bɔr umesuwe itsingo uwe uwu Unum.
\v 8 Ungo uba umesuwe iyorngo iwe ikerketangge, iwengge ru ungwɛ̃rhũ ugarh, bɔr, ungo uba umesuwe itsingo ri idɔsu Unum iwu ru ugarh ra abina kishoo. Awuri iyikake ungo ri ibibɛk icɛrɛ nu ibibɛk iyi unuma ungo uba ukpeɔ.
\p 
\v 9 Akɛrɛ awu idzidzɛrhayɛ iki imɛ̃ iyiyɛi kishoo.
\v 10 Umɛn itɔ̃ ni itɛ̃wã, ubinkutsu umɛn ifosa ru Unum uwu urhɛ, uwuruwi aka awu ififɔrh anera kishoo, undzumunga ra abirabɛ aka awe ru imangmang.
\p 
\v 11 Utsu nu umesuwe akɛrɛ ha.
\v 12 Niba uneke unera akwɛɛrka ungo ubinkutsu ungo uwu ungwɛ̃dzɛm, bɔr uwu ubin ukpuku umesa ra abika adɔsa ru arherhango, ru ibibɛkngo, ru ibibemango, ru imangmango, nu isisarngo.
\v 13 Utsɛku umum iki ĩba, utsu itsingo ri ivarhuwe Arherhu-Num ra anera ra awia, udzowe isarhe nu umesuwe.
\v 14 Niba ukwɛɛrkɔ izũwãyɛ Unum aka adzaa ru ungo ri isɔm Arherhu-Num ri ivang anggbaashi akakũ aka atsorhuwa abok nu ungo.
\v 15 Udzowe itsingo ri ikorhe akɛrɛ ha, ngge itsú anera kishoo anyã igha inggbaashingo.
\v 16 Ungwɛ̃dzɛn nggu ibibɛkngo nu imesango ikɛi. Ubima ra ake, ubinkutsu ungo uba ukorhungo, ungo uwuri ifɔrhɔ itsingo nu abika agũna ungo.
\c 5
\s1 Idzowe itsũwã ra atsɛ̃rhãpfu, // akakũ na agãrhã
\p 
\v 1 Niba utsɛrungo ukukũ ri itsoo, bɔr urherhe nggu unga ru nyaka ungo uku irherhe nggu utɛngo. Unyanga awɛdzɛm ru nyaka angwɛ̃mbi,
\v 2 nu unyanga ayɛtsɛrhkũ ru nyaka ayii, akatsɛrh ru nyaka anapumbi nggu undzumu isisar.
\p 
\v 3 Udzowe imor ra atsɛ̃rhãpfu abirabɛ aka ashimbɔ ra abika iyike.
\v 4 Bɔr utsɛ̃rhãpfu aba awea ra awɛkaci use angwɛ̃nungwɛ̃, umbɔ amesi idɛyiwe idzowe atsimbɔ ru Unum ri iyike abi iyambɔ. Ikorhe rimi hã umbɔ afase atesmbɔ ngge idɔɔte amɛn Unum.
\v 5 Utsɛ̃rhãpfuwi aka awe ri ibibee na ashia ru uner, unga afosa ru Unum na anu ifɛn-Num utsuu nu atenum, na arhusu Unum ayike.
\v 6 Bɔr utsɛ̃rhãpfuwi aka atsu amɛnnga ri ibee igũibɛn aka akpea ri ipfu, uko unga awu nggu urhɛ.
\v 7 Udzowe anera arherhe akɛrɛ igambɔ, ngge itsú umbɔ akorha abin aka arhika.
\v 8 Ubɛn unera aba asi iyikuka anernga, nu undzuma abi iyanga, unga aka atsɛyi imangmang hã. Ikpũ abi ha abewe anangmbɔ abi aka asheri imangmang.
\p 
\v 9 Ungo ukpurhu utsɛng itsok utsɛ̃rhãpfu ha ra atsok atsɛ̃rhãpfu imɛknga iba iki itsĩngge isɔka utɔ̃ĩ (60). Ikɛi na asisei idzidzɛrhe nggu utsaknga,
\v 10 na ahwɛngmbɔ itsernga iyiki ize, ru nyaki ikpɔm angwɛ̃nga ru utsĩndĩ uku uze, ayɛi atsen, asorhuka adak abika adɔsa, ayikuka abika abubee, ikɛi adzowe itsinga ri ikorhi iyiki ize.
\p 
\v 11 Anadzɛm aka awu atsɛ̃rhãpfu, niba utsukɔ atsokmbɔ ra atsok akɛrɛ, ubinkutsu ivang anyɔna akatsak aki igashuwe amɛnmbɔ nggu Ukiristo, umbɔ akpurha abee ipfuna.
\v 12 Akɛrɛ ha atsu umbɔ atsuyiwe atsimbɔ uvau, ubinkutsu, umbɔ aka azharhukumbɔ ibibemuwembɔ iyi inggbaashia.
\v 13 Asi iwea rimi ukpekũ, akɛrɛ ha atsu umbɔ aka isaka amesumbɔ isei ibɛm, na ayarhe atsĩrhã aya. Asi iwea isei ibɛm ukpekũ bɔr awu imesi ivɛrhe na atsĩrhã angwĩ arherhe abin aka asi imɛ̃ɛ̃ke.
\v 14 Nggee umum ibee anadzɛm atsɛ̃rhãpfu apfuna atsak, amar awɛkaci, akpɔm ayambɔ na akɛn anggamtsakmɛn ugarh ukpuku urherhi iyiki ibewe ra atsimɛn.
\v 15 Idzidzɛrhe abɔɔ aka adzipa adɔsu Ushaitan.
\p 
\v 16 Ubɛn ukutsɛrh uwuku udɔsawi aka awea ru utsɛ̃rhãpfu ra abi iyambɔ, unga ayike umbɔ utsur umbɔ atsukukumbɔ imor ri ikikɔng abika adɔsa. Ngge itsú abika adɔsa akpo ugarh ayike atsɛ̃rhãpfu abika abubee aka ashimbɔ ru uner.
\p 
\v 17 Akakũ abika adarh itser ikikɔng abika adɔsa izeize amɛ̃mbɔ iyɛi imor idiki ivaa, undzumunga abirabɛ itsermbɔ iki iwu iyi udũwã nu imesa.
\v 18 Ubinkutsu itsɛng Arherhu-Num igɔr igɛ, <<Niba ubvurkɔ angwĩ inak iyiki itsak ri ivangyɛ ngge iki idɛ̃ɛ̃ isung abin,>>\f + \fr 5.18 \ft Àka anyã ikɛi: \xt Iva 25.4\xt*\ft .\f* ikɛi <<Uner itser amɛ̃ɛ̃ iyɛi ugbɛtanga.>>\f + \fr 5.18 \ft Àka anyã ikɛi: \xt Irh 10.7\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 19 Niba uyɛsɔ arherhe aka abewe umbɔ aka itsu ri itsi ukukũ uwu ikikɔng abika adɔsa. Ungo ukpurhu uyɛi nggu ideka anera avaa use ataar.
\v 20 Ukukũ hã aba akorhunga arhim utsɛrha unga ra asu anera. Ngge itsú abɔɔ agũ iwei.
\p 
\v 21 Umum ĩdzaango itsũwã, ra asu Unum nu Ukiristo Uyesu nu ípfu itser-Numyɛ umbɔ aka asɛng, udɔsa akɛrɛ niba utsukɔ itɛngasu, use ibemu uwɔɔ unango uwɔɔ.
\p 
\v 22 Niba uzango itsorhuwe abok nu unera ri itsũ unga awu unggbaashi, ikɛi niba utsukɔ itsingo ra arhim abɔɔ. Utsam itsingo asarsatawɔ.
\p 
\v 23 Uneke ihwa amɛ̃ ukpekũ, bɔr uhwa amɛ̃ inebi ukunjiir ri itsi anango nu írhãrhãyɛ iki ighong ungo ubɛn ivang.
\p 
\v 24 Arhim abɔɔ awu ra awiya, aka ahwɛngmbɔ ake ru umbɔ adɔrha aviri ikikorhambɔ. Bɔr arhim abɔɔ ana awuwɔk utsɛku ivang iyɔɔ ake awuri idzekake.
\v 25 Rimi hã, itser iyiki ize abɔɔ iwu ra awiya, uko itser iyiki izeyɛ iki iwɔk, ngge iwuri idzekangge ri irhirhang.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Kishoo abika awe ru ukhɔɔ igãrhã adzowe ateiyambɔ undzumu imoryɛ iki imɛ̃, ngge itsú anera aneke irherhe iki ibewe ri itsok Unum nu imesamɛn.
\v 2 Agãrhãbɛ ateiyambɔ aka awu abika adɔsa, niba ikwɛɛrkumbɔ ateiyambɔ ugɛ umbɔ awu abika adɔsa. Nu ngge iki iwe rimi, imɛ̃ngge umbɔ atoma atɔ̃ itser iyiki ize, ubinkutsu abika agha ugarh itsermbɔ awu abika adɔsa ikɛi abirabɛ umbɔ aka abema. Awu ufang ungo umesuwe nu udzowe itsũwã ra abina akɛrɛ.
\s1 Ibemu uhwɛk
\p 
\v 3 Uba ubɛn unera aka amesuwe igbɛrangwĩ iyɔɔ iki isi iwengge ishaa arherhu Uteijee Uyesu Ukiristo nu imesayɛ iki iwe ri idɔsu Unum,
\v 4 uner ha awuri iberi itsi, asi íhwɛnga ubin. Awu ra amɛn aka abewe, ibee uning nggu irhɛm iyiki itsu unyɛ̃ɛ̃, nu uning, nu inyar nu ifɛrhkɔ iyiki ibewe ri itsi abɔɔ.
\v 5 Unga abee uning nggu abirabɛ ifɛrhkɔmbɔ iki ikpengge, idzidzɛrhe ikɛi ishingge ru umbɔ. Ikpũ abɛrɛ ha anyã idɔsu Unum iwu utsĩndĩ uwuku ukpo uhwɛk.
\p 
\v 6 Bɔr idɔsu Unum nggu ashur iwu ighigha,
\v 7 ubinkutsu, umɛn isi ikũ ubin itsĩwãmɛn ru upfung, ikɛi umɛn isi ídɛ̃ɛ̃ ikũ ubin idzemɛn ru ukpɔ.
\v 8 Bɔr umɛn ĩba iwemɛn ru ubingha nu atorho aka atsim, akɛrɛ ha amɛ̃ɛ̃ mɔnɔ.
\v 9 Abirabɛ aka abee iwu ru ubin aka isaka atsĩ ra andeya nu unggurhi, atsĩ urhɛrhɛ ikponi iyiki itãrhã, iki ikũ umbɔ izĩ itsitsim.
\v 10 Ubinkutsu ibemu uhwɛk ngge iwu usu irhɛ ikpũ iki ibewe. Ikponu uhwɛk itsu abɔɔ ayapumbɔ ri imangmangmbɔ utsɛku umbɔ aka atsu atsimbɔ ri ighongamɛn irhɛirhɛ.
\s1 Itsũwã Uburhu ru Utimoti
\p 
\v 11 Bɔr ungo, uner Unum, utĩɔ abina akɛrɛ kishoo. Utsu itsingo ubee irhirhika, ni idɔsu Unum, imangmang, ibibema, ibibima, nu ididɔɔr.
\v 12 Nu ununuka uwuku uze uwu imangmang. Ukpɔm itosa iyi urhɛ uwu ugbagbaa uwuruwi umbɔ aka ayisa ungo udzowe ideka iyiki ize ra asu abi ideka arhɛrhɛ.
\v 13 Umum itsu ungo ra asu Unum, uwuku udzowe urhɛ ra abina kishoo, nu Ukiristo Uyesu uwuruwi ri idekanga ra asu Ubuntu Ubirhatu aka arherhi idzidzɛrhe,
\v 14 udɔsu ubin hã Unum aka arherhe uku kpengkpeng utsɛku ibiba Uteijee Uyesu Ukiristo.
\v 15 Unum awuri ikũ unga adzeka ri ivanga iki irhika. Unum uwu idorh ha, unga ukpekũ awu ru ijee kishoo, awu Uyɛrhe ayɛrhe nu Uteijee ateijee.
\v 16 Unga ikiyikanga asi íkpea, unga awu ri irhirhangyɛ unera asi ídɛ̃ɛ̃ akhapunga umɔ, unera anasi inyãã use adɛ̃ɛ̃ anyãã. Ru unga imor nu iyɛrhe iwu ugbagbaa. Iwerimi.
\s1 Abika adɔsu Uyesu abika awu ru ubin
\p 
\v 17 Udɛyiwe abika awu ru ubin ru upfung ukpirɛ umbɔ niba aberumbɔ atsimbɔ use atsumbɔ amɛnmbɔ ri iwu ru ubin, akirakɛ aka asi ídãrhũke. Bɔr atsu amɛnmbɔ ru Unum, unga iki idzaa umɛn abina kishoo izũwã umɛn igũibɛn.
\v 18 Utsuke umbɔ akorhe iyiki ize, na awu ru ubin ri ikorhi iyiki ize, na awu abika ayanga abokmbɔ adzowe izũwã ayike abɔɔ.
\v 19 Ikorhe rimi hã umbɔ angwɛ̃we abinmbɔ akika awu atarh idzin ibibɛkmbɔ ru urhɛ uwuku iba unuma, ngge itsú umbɔ akpɔm urhɛwi uku uwu ishaa urhɛ.
\s1 Imimasha arherhe
\p 
\v 20 A Utimoti, ukpɔm ubinkpi umbɔ aka adzaa ungo idzɛu. Utsũwe itsingo ra arherhe aka atãrhã aka ashike ri iwei Unum, aki abɔɔ aka anyanga ugɛ awu idzursu bɔr isi iwengge rimi.
\v 21 Abɔɔ aka ayapumbɔ ru utsĩndĩ imangmang ri idɔsa arherha akɛrɛ.
\p Imimuta ima iwe nggu umbi.
